===Etymology===

From the [[hanja]]:  [[靑]] (청, ''cheong'', "blue") + [[鼠]] (''seo'', "rat") + [[毛]] (''mo'', "fur")

===Noun===

'''청설모''' (cheong.seol.mo)

# a [[red squirrel]], ''[[Sciurus vulgaris]]''.

# the fur of a squirrel.


